While we can see many examples, such as that of the girlfriend who easily understands at the sight of the morning photos, taken by the circle of mutual friends, with whom her unfaithful friend spent the evening, or that of the company that dismissed one of its employees, just for the sincere opinions that this one wrote on his blog about top management, we can be sure of one thing: the term privacy is totally to be reconsidered from These days.
