According to one of the company&#39;s internal rules, new services are not announced until they can be used. What is certain is that in the coming months and years, they will move the world to new points. While some think that Google&#39;s book and magazine scanning and archiving project is getting so big that the company will soon find itself facing the United States Supreme Court, others tremble before its system. Health, because in it, we can build a complete medical profit from our previous analysis results, doctors and problems.
